cc:Work.dc:title: NASA seal
cc:Work.dc:description: NASA seal imported from official SEAL-CL.EPS (Encapsulated PostScript) file. PostScript does not support gradient fills, so they are simulated step-wise and may cause aliasing effects at various zoom factors. The blue background disk in this Inkscape version has been replaced by a linear gradient fill, but the shadows on the two "spheres" are still stepped gradients.
